Package: BikeWise
Type: Package
Title: Bike Safe and Dry
Version: 0.1.0
URL: https://github.com/sebkrbs/BikeWise
BugReports: https://github.com/sebkrbs/BikeWise/issues
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Sebastian", "Krebs",
      email = "sebasti.k24@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Plans a cycling route between two locations and checks the weather
    along the way to suggest the safest time to leave. Helps cyclists avoid rain
    by finding the next dry departure window within a 24-hour forecast.
